{"type":null,"faqId":33870,"title":"如何使用亲情关怀功能？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请按如下步骤操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 1.在主屏幕，点击手机服务。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 2.进入亲情关怀，点击远程协助。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 3.根据屏幕提示，点击立即启用，启用该服务。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 4.点击添加亲友团。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 5.从联系人列表中勾选要添加的亲友，然后点击勾选图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 6.根据需要，选择发起邀请或者发起请求。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\"> 7.根据屏幕提示，双方建立远程连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">需要对方手机也支持亲情关怀，目前华为大多数手机可以在华为应用市场下载“亲情关怀”来配合使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8572","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748751000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":43,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"亲情关怀","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}